############################################### Tools & Software ##############################################################

########## Code ##########
##### AWS #####
https://github.com/wallix/awless - A Mighty CLI for AWS
https://github.com/jfaerman/aws-daleks - Iterate and exterminate an AWS Account
https://github.com/awslabs/aws-serverless-java-container - Java wrapper to run Spring,Jersey, Spark other apps inside AWS Lambda
https://github.com/aws/chalice - Python Serverless Microframework for AWS
https://github.com/alexandres/poormanscdn -  a caching proxy to Amazon S3 with automatic HTTPS
https://github.com/stojanovic/scottyjs - Deploy static websites and single page apps to AWS S3 and CloudFront


##### Docker #####
https://github.com/dollarshaveclub/furan - Scale out Docker builds
https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/distroless -  Language focused docker images, minus the operating system.


###### Kubernetes #####
https://github.com/bjhaid/pam_hook - Pam based webhook authentication for Kubernetes
https://github.com/garethr/kubeval - Validate your Kubernetes configuration files
https://github.com/kelseyhightower/kubernetes-initializer-tutorial - Tutorial for building and deploying Kubernetes Initializers
https://github.com/Shopify/kubernetes-deploy -  command-line tool that helps you ship changes to a Kubernetes namespace
https://github.com/heptio/sonobuoy  - a diagnostic tool that makes it easier to understand the state of a Kubernetes cluster


