https://github.com/gp187/nginx-builder - A bash script & GUI interface to make adding modules and building nginx easy
https://github.com/lipp/login-with - Stateless login-with microservice for OAuth
https://github.com/shieldfy/API-Security-Checklist - Security Checklist
https://github.com/jessfraz/binctr - Fully static, unprivileged, self-contained, containers as executable binaries
https://github.com/paragonie/sapient - Secure API Toolkit 
https://github.com/lavabit/magma - an encrypted email system with support for SMTP, POP, IMAP, HTTP and MOLTEN
https://github.com/firehol/netdata - Get control of your servers. Simple. Effective. Awesome
https://github.com/dthree/addict - Get a full Active Directory REST API in 30 seconds
https://github.com/dthree/mailit - A tiny drop-in REST API to send emails



